  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "忍者龍剣伝III。シリーズ完結編。最高難度の挑戦。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Thrilling new cinema screen! Follow the story of Ryu's epic adventure through Tecmo's movie-like Cinema Screen Animation. As you complete each level, a new part of the story unfolds. Exciting new powers and weapons! Over the years Ninja Ryu's fighting skills have improved to include fantastic new powers and weapons. Action-packed Ninja adventure! Can you get Ryu through his most challenging adventure as he battles the hideous ancient forces of darkness to save mankind? The Ultimate Ninja Challenge!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
